OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FZayn opens up about One    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FDirection split            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Zayn Malik has revealed the reasons    
OL,6, behind his abrupt departure from One   
OL,7, Direction in his first interview for   
OL,8, six years.                             
OL,10,FThe star quit the band in the middle of
OL,11,Ftheir 2015 world tour, initially saying
OL,12,Fhe had taken a break due to "stress".  
OL,14,FBut speaking to the Call Her Daddy     
OL,15,Fpodcast, Zayn said he'd realised the   
OL,16,Fband's days were numbered when other   
OL,17,Fmembers refused to sign new contracts. 
OL,19,F"I knew something was happening, so I  
OL,20,Fjust got ahead of the curve," he said. 
